(92, 6, '2023-02-27 11:57:26', '2023-02-27 11:57:26', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Controversial actress, Kangana Ranaut recently took to social media once again to call out Bollywood, for treating her like an outsider. The \"Queen\" actress claimed that she made a name for herself without any assistance from others. In a series of tweets, she claimed that the Hindi film industry has cast her aside because she refused to comply with their commands.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\"This Bollywood industry has called me out as full of attitude and arrogance, they simply wanted to use me as a pawn and make me do item numbers at weddings. They called me names and declared me mad, because I don\'t giggle and gossip like other girls or dance in weddings or want to go to heroes\' rooms!! Is this the reason why someone should be targeted, harassed or isolated?\" read the post.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Kangana Ranaut says she was ‘declared mad’ by movie mafia', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '82-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-02-27 11:57:26', '2023-02-27 11:57:26', '', 82, 'http://192.168.54.118/Round53/wordpress/saptahik-chitkar/?p=92', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
